sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Sidecar as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant CaikitHTTP as Caikit Runtime (HTTP)<br/>8080/TCP
    participant CaikitGRPC as Caikit Runtime (gRPC)<br/>8085/TCP
    participant TGIS as TGIS Inference Engine<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus UWM<br/>8086/TCP

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 1: HTTP Text Generation Inference

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward request<br/>mTLS envelope<br/>HTTP/8080
    Sidecar->>CaikitHTTP: HTTP request<br/>Loopback/8080<br/>No encryption (sidecar-to-app)
    CaikitHTTP->>TGIS: gRPC inference request<br/>Loopback/8033<br/>No encryption (localhost)
    TGIS-->>CaikitHTTP: Inference result
    CaikitHTTP-->>Sidecar: HTTP response
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: mTLS response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: HTTP Streaming Text Generation

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/server-streaming-text-generation<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward request<br/>mTLS/8080
    Sidecar->>CaikitHTTP: HTTP request<br/>Loopback/8080
    CaikitHTTP->>TGIS: gRPC streaming request<br/>Loopback/8033
    loop Streaming tokens
        TGIS-->>CaikitHTTP: Token chunk
        CaikitHTTP-->>Sidecar: SSE event
        Sidecar-->>Gateway: mTLS stream
        Gateway-->>Client: SSE token
    end

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 3: gRPC Inference

    Client->>Gateway: gRPC caikit.runtime.Nlp<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>HTTPS/443 (h2c passthrough)
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward request<br/>mTLS/gRPC/8085
    Sidecar->>CaikitGRPC: gRPC request<br/>Loopback/8085
    CaikitGRPC->>TGIS: gRPC inference request<br/>Loopback/8033
    TGIS-->>CaikitGRPC: Inference result
    CaikitGRPC-->>Sidecar: gRPC response
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: mTLS response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Prometheus,CaikitHTTP: Flow 4: Metrics Scraping

    Prometheus->>CaikitHTTP: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086<br/>PERMISSIVE mTLS<br/>(plaintext allowed)
    CaikitHTTP-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
